article.description: — Will Baker scored 20 points as Nevada beat Akron 62-58 on Wednesday night at the Cayman Islands Classic.
article.headline: Baker scores 20 as Nevada defeats Akron 62-58
article.linkText: Baker scores 20 as Nevada defeats Akron 62-58
article.story: GEORGE TOWN, Cayman Islands -- — Will Baker scored 20 points as Nevada beat Akron 62-58 on Wednesday night at the Cayman Islands Classic. Baker added six rebounds for the Wolf Pack (6-1). Jarod Lucas scored 16 points while shooting 5 for 15, including 4 for 9 from beyond the arc. Kenan Blackshear shot 3 of 7 from the field and 3 for 4 from the line to finish with 10 points. Tavari Johnson finished with 21 points, four assists and two steals for the Zips (3-3). Akron also got 11 points from Xavier Castaneda. Enrique Freeman finished with nine points and nine rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
